# Install Steps
https://github.com/blackducksoftware/hub/tree/master/kubernetes/blackduck
If Custom TLS Secret are not using use the below command
helm install ${BD_NAME} synopsys/blackduck --namespace ${BD_NAME} --no-hooks
Source:https://github.com/cert-manager/cert-manager/issues/5217#issuecomment-1157783671

kubectl config set-context --current --namespace=my-namespace
